<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/page_actions.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/page_actions.tpl) -->
    <!--Content-Begin-->
    <article>
      <h1>Overgang til nyt måleinstrumentdirektiv (MID)</h1>
      <summary>
        <p>
        
                  
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl) -->

Se spørgsmål og svar om måleinstrumentdirektivet.
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl) -->
                </p>
      </summary>
      <hr>

          
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
<div class="faq-item">
  <div class="question hover">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Anmodning om overensstemmelsesvurdering er sendt til et bemyndiget organ før 20. april 2016. Vil måleinstrumentet blive vurderet efter det gamle direktiv uanset om processen afsluttes før eller efter 20. april 2016?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
  <div class="answer">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Det er datoen på overensstemmelseserklæringen, der er afgørende for, hvilket direktiv måleinstrumentet skal leve op til. Overensstemmelsesvurderingen skal derfor være afsluttet inden 20. april 2016 (BÅDE fx Modul B og D) og måleinstrumentet skal være bragt i omsætning, dvs. være leveret fra fabrikanten hvis instrumentet skal vurderes efter det gamle direktiv.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
          
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
<div class="faq-item">
  <div class="question hover">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Skal måleinstrumentet leve op til det nye direktiv, når EF-typeafprøvningsattesten (efter modul B) skal forlænges ved udløb efter 10 år?&nbsp;</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
  <div class="answer">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Et måleinstrument der er fremstillet efter det gamle direktiv er stadig i overensstemmelse med de væsentlige krav i det nye direktiv og kan fortsat bringes i omsætning indtil udløbet af gyldighedsperioden for certifikatet.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Hvis der sker ændringer af den standard instrumentet er EF- typeoverensstemmelsvurderet efter, kan EF-typeafprøvningsattesten ikke forlænges ved udløb efter 10 år, men skal bringes i overensstemmelse med den nye standard.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
          
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
<div class="faq-item">
  <div class="question hover">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Hvis et måleinstrument modificeres efter ibrugtagning og efter 20. april 2016, skal det så leve op til kravene efter det nye direktiv?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
  <div class="answer">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Ja, hvis et måleinstrument modificeres, skal der udarbejdes en ny overensstemmelseserklæring. Hvis det sker efter 20. april 2016, skal overensstemmelseserklæringen referere til det nye direktiv.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Der er tale om en modificering, hvis ændringen vil medføre, at måleinstrumentets oprindelige ydeevne, formål og type ændres. Ved modificeringer kræves en ny overensstemmelsesvurdering, og den der tager ansvaret for modificeringerne vil blive anset som fabrikant og pålagt fabrikantens forpligtigelser.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
          
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
<div class="faq-item">
  <div class="question hover">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Skal overensstemmelseserklæringer på måleinstrumenter, der har været bragt i omsætning før 20. april 2016 opdateres, hvis måleinstrumenterne fortsat bringes i omsætning efter 20. april 2016?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
  <div class="answer">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

Hvis fabrikanten i sin overensstemmelseserklæring fra før 20. april 2016 har indsat en sætning som denne:<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

“The object of the declaration described above is in conformity with the relevant Union harmonisation legislation: Directive 2004/22/EF (until 19 April 2016) and Directive 2014/32/EU (from 20 April 2016).”<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

så er der ikke behov for at udfærdige en ny overensstemmelseserklæring. <br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

&nbsp;<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

Hvis fabrikanten alene har en overensstemmelseserklæring, hvor der står:<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

“The object of the declaration described above is in conformity with the relevant Union harmonisation legislation: Directive 2004/22/EF” <br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

så skal der pr. 20. april 2016 udfærdiges en ny erklæring, hvori der står:<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

“The object of the declaration described above is in conformity with the relevant Union harmonisation legislation: Directive 2014/32/EU” <br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Fabrikanten kan i denne nye erklæring fortsat henvise til den typeafprøvningsattest, der findes i henhold til Direktiv 2004/22/EF.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
          
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
<div class="faq-item">
  <div class="question hover">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Nogle landes bemyndigede organer kræver, at måleinstrumenter vurderes på ny, hvis der kommer ændringer i vurderingsgrundlaget, fx at en harmoniseret standard ændres. Gælder dette også i Danmark?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
  <div class="answer">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Måleinstrumentet skal leve op til de krav, der var gældende på det tidspunkt, hvor det blev bragt i omsætning. Dette er gældende både for MID og NAWI, når der ikke står andet i overgangsbestemmelserne.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
          
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
<div class="faq-item">
  <div class="question hover">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Af fx MID 2014/32/EU bilag II Modul B pkt. 3 fremgår det, at den tekniske dokumentation skal omfatte en fyldestgørende analyse og vurdering af risikoen/risiciene. Hvad er kravene og omfanget af dette?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
  <div class="answer">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Det vil være en individuel vurdering, hvor omfattende en sådan risikoanalyse og vurdering skal være. Det bemyndigede organ afgør om den er fyldestgørende. En risikoanalyse og vurdering kan blot bestå af en erklæring om, at den harmoniserede standard, der er anvendt, dækker alle risici, der vil kunne forekomme ved måleinstrumentet. Der kan også være krav om, at der udarbejdes en fuld risikoanalyse uanset om standarden tager højde for det. Der er i direktivet ikke formkrav til en sådan risikoanalyse, men det bemyndigede organ kan have krav til anvendelse af et bestemt format.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Sikkerhedsstyrelsen vil følge udviklingen i hvilke krav, der stilles og efter behov tage en eventuel problemstilling op i Kommissionens ekspertgruppe, der evaluerer MID og NAWI.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
    
    </article>
    <!--Content-End-->
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-3">
    
